e fields are included in the form<\\/li>\\n<li>Tweak: Add entry and action to frm_autoresponder_time hook<\\/li>\\n<li>Tweak: Change naming to Automation instead of Autoresponder to indicate expanded functionality<\\/li>\\n<li>Tweak: Large refactoring in the code behind the scenes<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Show the queued time in the current site timezone<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix: Remove queued events when an entry is deleted<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n\",\"plugin\":\"formidable-autoresponder\\/formidable-autoresponder.php\",\"icons\":{\"1x\":\"https:\\/\\/ps.w.org\\/formidable\\/assets\\/icon-256x256.png\"},\"banners\":{\"high\":\"https:\\/\\/ps.w.org\\/formidable\\/assets\\/banner-1544x500.png\",\"low\":\"https:\\/\\/ps.w.org\\/formidable\\/assets\\/banner-1544x500.png\"},\"search_terms\":\"automate, automation\",\"expires\":\"1654300799\",\"code\":\"valid\",\"date\":\"2018-11-28 19:20:00\",\"type\":\"elite\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/s3.amazonaws.com\\/fp.strategy11.com\\/releases\\/autoresponder\\/formidable-autoresponder-2.04.zip?AWSAccessKeyId=AKIAJ3QHAN4BJMSYZ3ZQ&Expires=1648626691&Signature=DkkOJmIy2caK%2B9lknGbbGXkuqeg%3D\",\"timeout\":1648626691,\"package\":\"https:\\/\\/s3.amazonaws.com\\/fp.strategy11.com\\/releases\\/autoresponder\\/formidable-autoresponder-2.04.zip?AWSAccessKeyId=AKIAJ3QHAN4BJMSYZ3ZQ&Expires=1648626691&Signature=DkkOJmIy2caK%2B9lknGbbGXkuqeg%3D\"},\"168072\":{\"title\":\"Formidable API\",\"name\":\"Formidable API\",\"slug\":\"formidable-api\",\"version\":\"1.11\",\"new_version\":\"1.11\",\"excerpt\":\"Add a full forms API for forms, form fields, views, and entries. Then send submissions to other sites with REST APIs.\",\"id\":168072,\"released\":\"2016-06-08 00:00:00\",\"categories\":[\"Business\",\"Strategy11\"],\"docs\":\"\\/knowledgebase\\/formidable-api\\/\",\"link\":\"https:\\/\\/formidableforms.com\\/downloads\\/formidable-api\\/\",\"changelog\":\"<h4>v1.11 - March 16, 2022<\\/h4>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Fix: Fixed \\\"frm_js is not defined\\\" console error that was 