a koju iz godine u godinu unapređujemo i nadograđujemo.\r\n\r\nOd 2020. godine smo započeli proširivanje delovanja u okviru delatnosti. Naše znanje i iskustvo smo povezali i proširili na prodaju. Prodaja se odnosi na dekorativne tehnike i materijale, kao i prodaju dekorativnih tapeta viskokog kvaliteta. Prodaju i distribuciju vršimo putem sajta i u našem izložbenom salonu koji se nalazi na bulevaru cara Lazara 74 u Novom Sadu. Dođite kod nas i uverite se u kvalitet naših proizvoda i usluga.'),(634,14,'_flexible_4_add_main_content','field_6230a16e842f8'),(635,14,'flexible_4_add_page_link','19'),(636,14,'_flexible_4_add_page_link','field_6230a245f02e7'),(637,14,'flexible_4_active','1'),(638,14,'_flexible_4_active','field_622faa95d472c'),(639,148,'flexible','a:5:{i:0;s:18:\"hero_section_large\";i:1;s:25:\"our_most_popular_products\";i:2;s:13:\"our_portfolio\";i:3;s:12:\"our_services\";i:4;s:18:\"image_text_section\";}'),(640,148,'_flexible','field_622b56d1d5848'),(641,148,'flexible_0_choose_slider_products','a:3:{i:0;s:2:\"59\";i:1;s:2:\"54\";i:2;s:2:\"68\";}'),(642,148,'_flexible_0_choose_slider_products','field_622b56efd5849'),(643,148,'flexible_0_active','1'),(644,148,'_flexible_0_active','field_622b57bcd584c'),(645,148,'flexible_1_title_label',''),(646,148,'_flexible_1_title_label','field_622fbe79505f3'),(647,148,'flexible_1_main_title','Najpopularniji proizvodi'),(648,148,'_flexible_1_main_title','field_622fbe79505f4'),(649,148,'flexible_1_section_description','Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit'),(650,148,'_flexible_1_section_description','field_622fbe79505f5'),(651,148,'flexible_1_choose_most_popular_products','a:6:{i:0;s:2:\"54\";i:1;s:2:\"56\";i:2;s:2:\"59\";i:3;s:2:\"63\";i:4;s:2:\"68\";i:5;s:2:\"66\";}'),(652,148,'_flexible_1_choose_most_popular_products','field_622fbe79505f6'),(653,148,'flexible_1_butt